title: Winnipeg Jets VS Detroit Red Wings in Game 3 of the 1996 Stanley
description:
This is the Winnipeg Jets VS Detroit Red Wings in the 3rd game of the 1996 Stanley Cup Playoffs. This would be the last Jets win at home at the Winnipeg Arena and is certainly in the 10 top Winnipeg Jets games played there of all time. The Winnipeg white-out is known around the world and this game is certainly a fine example of the enthusiasm and class the Winnipeg Jets had throughout their time in the city of Winnipeg. 

The NHL will return to Winnipeg soon but, in the meantime; sit back and enjoy and another Winnipeg Jets Classic Game.
